        <updateDate>2007-08-10T14:47:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Public Safety Tax Cut Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow full-time police officers or firefighters a tax credit of $1,000; and (2) exclude from the gross income of volunteer police officers or firefighters certain public services benefits received from a state or local government agency. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
